            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 7 min or until the spring greens have wilted and the meat-free bacon<strong> </strong>is warmed through – this is your <strong>roasted pepper & plant-based bacon tray bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
